---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout 
  title="Porcelain Veneers" 
  category="Cosmetic Dentistry"
  description="These are thin layers bonded directly to a damaged tooth to help achieve a natural looking smile. This is ideal for minor chips or cracks in teeth."
  image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1609207825181-52d3214556dd?w=1920&h=600&fit=crop"
>
  
  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-100 to-accent-200/50 border-l-4 border-accent-300 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Transform Your Smile</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-0">
        These are thin layers bonded directly to a damaged tooth to help achieve a natural looking smile. 
        This is ideal for minor chips or cracks in teeth. Porcelain veneers can also address discoloration, 
        gaps, and shape irregularities for a perfect smile makeover.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      What Are Porcelain Veneers?
    </h2>
    
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Porcelain veneers are ultra-thin, custom-made shells crafted from high-quality dental porcelain. 
            They're designed to cover the front surface of teeth, transforming their color, shape, size, 
            and overall appearance. Each veneer is individually crafted to match your desired smile.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Key Characteristics</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Ultra-thin:</strong> Only 0.5-0.7mm thick (like a contact lens)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Natural-looking:</strong> Mimics light reflection of real teeth</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Stain-resistant:</strong> High-quality porcelain resists discoloration</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Custom-made:</strong> Each veneer designed specifically for you</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <span><strong>Durable:</strong> Can last 10-15+ years with proper care</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="w-72 h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-primary-200/30 rounded-lg shadow-md flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-32 h-32 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 00.95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 00-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 00-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 00-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.519-4.674z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Conditions Veneers Can Address
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <!-- Common Issues -->
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Cosmetic Concerns</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-red-600 text-xs font-bold">•</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Chips and Cracks</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Minor damage from accidents or wear</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-yellow-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-yellow-600 text-xs font-bold">•</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Discoloration</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Stains that don't respond to whitening</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-blue-600 text-xs font-bold">•</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Gaps Between Teeth</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Small spaces that affect smile appearance</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-purple-600 text-xs font-bold">•</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Worn Down Teeth</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Age-related wear or grinding damage</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Shape & Size Issues -->
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-4">Shape & Size Issues</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-green-600 text-xs font-bold">•</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Misshapen Teeth</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Irregular or asymmetrical tooth shapes</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-orange-600 text-xs font-bold">•</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Small or Short Teeth</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Teeth that appear too small for the smile</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-teal-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-teal-600 text-xs font-bold">•</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Minor Misalignment</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Slightly crooked teeth in visible areas</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-pink-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-pink-600 text-xs font-bold">•</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold">Uneven Tooth Lengths</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Creating a more uniform smile line</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      The Veneer Process
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6 mb-12">
      <!-- Consultation -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-2">Consultation & Planning</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              We discuss your goals, examine your teeth, and take photos and impressions. Using digital 
              smile design, we show you exactly how your new smile will look before treatment begins.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-primary-100 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <strong>Smile preview:</strong> See your results before committing to treatment
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Preparation -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-primary-900 font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Tooth Preparation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              A thin layer of enamel (about 0.5mm) is gently removed from the front of each tooth to make 
              room for the veneer. Local anesthetic ensures your comfort during this process.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-accent-100 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <strong>Minimal preparation:</strong> Preserves most of your natural tooth structure
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Impressions & Temporary Veneers -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-2">Impressions & Temporaries</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Precise impressions are taken and sent to our lab. Temporary veneers protect your teeth 
              and give you a preview of your new smile while permanent veneers are being crafted.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-primary-100 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <strong>Lab time:</strong> 1-2 weeks to create your custom porcelain veneers
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Final Placement -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-primary-900 font-bold">4</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Bonding & Final Adjustments</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Your custom veneers are carefully fitted, adjusted for perfect bite and appearance, 
              then permanently bonded to your teeth using advanced adhesive technology.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-accent-100 rounded-lg p-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <strong>Immediate results:</strong> See your transformation right away
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Veneers vs. Other Cosmetic Options
    </h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-12">
      <table class="w-full bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md">
        <thead class="bg-primary-100">
          <tr>
            <th class="px-6 py-4 text-left font-semibold text-primary-900">Treatment</th>
            <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-primary-900">Best For</th>
            <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-primary-900">Longevity</th>
            <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-primary-900">Tooth Preparation</th>
            <th class="px-6 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-primary-900">Cost Range</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
          <tr class="bg-accent-50">
            <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold text-primary-900">Porcelain Veneers</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-sm">Comprehensive smile makeovers</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-green-600">10-15+ years</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-orange-600">Minimal removal</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-sm">$800-2000 per tooth</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold">Teeth Whitening</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-sm">Discoloration only</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-yellow-600">1-3 years</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-green-600">None</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-sm">$300-800</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold">Dental Bonding</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-sm">Minor chips, small gaps</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-yellow-600">3-7 years</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-green-600">Minimal/None</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-sm">$150-400 per tooth</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold">Dental Crowns</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-sm">Heavily damaged teeth</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-green-600">10-20 years</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-red-600">Significant removal</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-sm">$800-1500 per tooth</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-gray-50">
            <td class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold">Invisalign</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-sm">Alignment issues</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-green-600">Permanent results</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-green-600">None</td>
            <td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-sm">$3000-8000 total</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Caring for Your Veneers
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-700 mb-4">Daily Care</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Brush with non-abrasive toothpaste</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Floss daily to prevent gum disease</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Use an alcohol-free mouthwash</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Regular dental checkups and cleanings</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-red-700 mb-4">Things to Avoid</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Biting or chewing on hard objects (ice, pens)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Using teeth as tools to open packages</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Grinding or clenching teeth (wear a night guard)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Excessive alcohol consumption (can weaken bond)</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Investment in Your Smile
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Value Considerations</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            While veneers represent a significant investment, they offer exceptional value when you 
            consider their longevity, natural appearance, and the confidence boost they provide.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-2">Long-term Investment</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                With proper care, veneers can last 10-15+ years, making the cost per year very reasonable
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-2">Immediate Transformation</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                Unlike other treatments that take months, you see dramatic results immediately
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Financing Options</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
